          "reviewBody": "* A good school indeed.\n1. Politeness is the face of humanity. And this is the characteristic of this school which can be seen in teachers and students as well.\n2. Academic and other activities are equally worked out on time.\n3, Active intelligent and disciplined staff  makes enthusiastic environment .\n4. Proper safety measures for children by using cameras, id cards checking and guards.\n5. A good principal.\n6. Perfect transport system.\n7. Hindu values and modern values are equally taught to students.\n* School has female staff maximum. It's good for child care and education. But parents are not much  close to teachers for communication 'bout their child. Precaution-meaaure in ncr may be the reason.\n* I hope school will produce achievers. Best wishes!",
